name: ExtensionDeviceMetric_Calibration
title: Cross-version Extension `R5.DeviceMetric.calibration` for use in FHIR R4
description: This cross-version extension represents the FHIR R5 element `DeviceMetric.calibration` for use in FHIR R4.
purpose:
This extension is part of the cross-version definitions generated to enable use of the
element `DeviceMetric.calibration` as defined in FHIR R5
in FHIR R4.

`DeviceMetric.calibration` 0..* `BackboneElement`

*  R5: `DeviceMetric.calibration` 0..* `BackboneElement`
*  R4B: `DeviceMetric.calibration` 0..* `BackboneElement`
*  R4: `DeviceMetric.calibration` 0..* `BackboneElement`
